headline: Walgreens shareholders approve $10B Sycamore acquisition
summary: The transaction, expected to close in Q3 or Q4, will take the company private after nearly 100 years as a public company.

headline: Walgreens acquisition by Sycamore wins shareholder agreement
summary: WBA shareholders will receive $11.45 per share in cash upon the deal's closure.
